Next / previous project (wraps around).
.TP
.BR 1 \(en 9
Jump to project by number.
.TP
.BR n \ or\  Enter
Open the prompt input (enter Prompt mode).
.TP
.B o
Open the directory picker modal to add a project (local or SSH).
.TP
.B x
Cancel the last running agent.
.TP
.B d
Detach the selected agent widget (saves its state for later reattachment).
.TP
.B r
Open the reattach menu for detached agents in the current project.
.TP
.B j
Scroll the agent panel down.
.TP
.B k
Scroll the agent panel up.
.TP
.B f
Toggle the file browser panel.
.TP
.B e
Toggle the read\-only editor panel.
.TP
.B i
Enter edit mode in the editor (editor must be visible first).
.TP
.B m
